in your mind?

00:06:44.090 --> 00:06:46.040
And how many people have actually seen a bald
eagle in

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:49.251
the wild. So even though not everybody has
seen one in

00:06:49.251 --> 00:06:56.000
the wild, they can picture a bald eagle. Those
experiences totally, totally determine every

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.290
time you go
click what that picture is going to be. Now,

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:01.280
here's the
whole trick in the thing. You don't get to

00:07:01.280 --> 00:07:04.290
